{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"I only have three minutes"},{"time":2000,"text":"so I'm going to have to talk fast, and it will"},{"time":4000,"text":"use up your spare mental cycles, so multitasking may be hard."},{"time":8000,"text":"So, 27 years ago I got a traffic ticket"},{"time":10000,"text":"that got me thinking."},{"time":12000,"text":"I've had some time to think it over."},{"time":14000,"text":"And energy efficiency is more than just"},{"time":16000,"text":"about the vehicle --"},{"time":18000,"text":"it's also about the road."}]},{"cues":[{"time":20000,"text":"Road design makes a difference, particularly intersections,"},{"time":22000,"text":"of which there are two types: signalized"},{"time":24000,"text":"and unsignalized, which means stop signs."},{"time":26000,"text":"Fifty percent of crashes happen at intersections."},{"time":28000,"text":"Roundabouts are much better."},{"time":30000,"text":"A study of 24 intersections"},{"time":32000,"text":"has found crashes drop 40 percent"},{"time":35000,"text":"from when you convert a traffic light into a roundabout."},{"time":38000,"text":"Injury crashes have dropped 76 percent,"},{"time":41000,"text":"fatal crashes down 90 percent."},{"time":43000,"text":"But that's just safety."},{"time":45000,"text":"What about time and gas?"},{"time":47000,"text":"So, traffic keeps flowing, so that means less braking,"},{"time":49000,"text":"which means less accelerating, less gas and less pollution,"},{"time":52000,"text":"less time wasted,"},{"time":54000,"text":"and that partly accounts for Europe's better efficiency"},{"time":56000,"text":"than we have in the United States."}]},{"cues":[{"time":58000,"text":"So, unsignalized intersections,"},{"time":60000,"text":"meaning stop signs, they save many lives,"},{"time":62000,"text":"but there's an excessive proliferation of them."},{"time":64000,"text":"Small roundabouts are starting to appear."},{"time":67000,"text":"This is one in my neighborhood. And they are"},{"time":70000,"text":"much better -- better than traffic lights, better than four-way stop signs."},{"time":73000,"text":"They're expensive to install,"},{"time":75000,"text":"but they are more expensive not to. So, we should look at that."}]},{"cues":[{"time":78000,"text":"But they are not applicable in all situations."},{"time":79000,"text":"So, take, for example, the three-way intersection."},{"time":82000,"text":"So, it's logical that you'd have one there,"},{"time":84000,"text":"on the minor road entering the major."},{"time":86000,"text":"But the other two are somewhat questionable."},{"time":89000,"text":"So, here's one. There's another one which I studied."},{"time":91000,"text":"Cars rarely appear on that third road."}]},{"cues":[{"time":94000,"text":"And so, the question is, what does that cost us?"},{"time":96000,"text":"That intersection I looked at had about 3,000"},{"time":98000,"text":"cars per day in each direction,"},{"time":100000,"text":"and so that's two ounces of gas to accelerate out of."},{"time":102000,"text":"That's five cents each, and times 3,000 cars per day,"},{"time":104000,"text":"that's $51,000 per year."},{"time":107000,"text":"That's just the gasoline cost. There is also pollution,"},{"time":109000,"text":"wear on the car, and time."},{"time":111000,"text":"What's that time worth?"},{"time":113000,"text":"Well, at 10 seconds per 3,000 cars,"},{"time":115000,"text":"that's 8.3 hours per day. The average wage in the U.S."},{"time":117000,"text":"is $20 an hour. That is 60,000 per year."},{"time":121000,"text":"Add that together with the gas, and it's $112,000 per year,"},{"time":124000,"text":"just for that sign in each direction."}]},{"cues":[{"time":126000,"text":"Discount that back to the present, at five percent:"},{"time":128000,"text":"over two million dollars"},{"time":131000,"text":"for a stop sign, in each direction."},{"time":134000,"text":"Now, if you look at what that adjacent property is worth,"},{"time":138000,"text":"you could actually buy the property,"},{"time":140000,"text":"cut down the shrubbery to improve the sight line,"},{"time":143000,"text":"and then sell it off again."},{"time":145000,"text":"And you'd still come out ahead."},{"time":147000,"text":"So, it makes one wonder, \"Why is it there?\""},{"time":149000,"text":"I mean, why is there that stop sign in each direction?"},{"time":152000,"text":"Because it is saving lives. So, is there a better way to accomplish that goal?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":155000,"text":"The answer is to enable cars"},{"time":157000,"text":"to come in from that side road safely."},{"time":159000,"text":"Because there are a lot of people who might live up there"},{"time":161000,"text":"and if they're waiting forever a long queue could form"},{"time":163000,"text":"because the cars aren't slowing down on the main road."},{"time":166000,"text":"Can that be accomplished with existing signs?"},{"time":168000,"text":"So, there is a long history of stop signs and yield signs."},{"time":171000,"text":"Stop signs were invented in 1915,"},{"time":173000,"text":"yield signs in 1950. But that's all we got."}]},{"cues":[{"time":176000,"text":"So, why not use a yield sign?"},{"time":178000,"text":"Well the meaning of yield is: You must yield the right-of-way."},{"time":181000,"text":"That means that if there are five cars waiting, you have to wait"},{"time":183000,"text":"till they all go, then you go. It lacks the notion"},{"time":185000,"text":"of alternating, or taking turns,"},{"time":187000,"text":"and it's always on the minor road,"},{"time":189000,"text":"allowing the major one to have primacy."},{"time":191000,"text":"So, it's hard to create a new meaning for the existing sign."},{"time":193000,"text":"You couldn't suddenly tell everyone, \"OK, remember"},{"time":195000,"text":"what you used to do at yield signs? Now do something different.\""},{"time":197000,"text":"That would not work."}]},{"cues":[{"time":199000,"text":"So, what the world needs now"},{"time":201000,"text":"is a new type of sign."},{"time":203000,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":207000,"text":"So, you'd have a little instruction below it,"},{"time":210000,"text":"you know, for those who didn't see the public service announcements."},{"time":212000,"text":"And it merges the stop sign and yield signs."},{"time":215000,"text":"It's kind of shaped like a T, as in taking turns."},{"time":217000,"text":"And uncertainty results in caution."},{"time":220000,"text":"When people come to an unfamiliar situation they don't know how to deal with"},{"time":222000,"text":"they slow down."}]},{"cues":[{"time":224000,"text":"So, now that you are all \"Road Scholars\" ..."},{"time":226000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":227000,"text":"don't wait for that sign to be adopted, these things don't change quickly."},{"time":230000,"text":"But you all are members of communities,"},{"time":232000,"text":"and you can exercise your community influence"},{"time":234000,"text":"to create more sensible traffic flows."},{"time":236000,"text":"And you can have more impact on the environment"},{"time":238000,"text":"just getting your neighborhood to change these things"},{"time":240000,"text":"than by changing your vehicle. Thank you very much."},{"time":243000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}